data.description: Breathtaking home above Lake Mead, nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac on a premium oversized lot! Charming courtyard leads you to a spacious living area that seamlessly connects to a backyard oasis. Master suite enjoys direct yard access. Revel in the pool, expansive sun cover, and outdoor entertainment patio. Extras include RV parking with a spacious pad and a 630 sqft garage. Mere minutes to trails, parks, Lake Mead Recreational area, and the historic Boulder City shops/eateries. A must-see gem in an exceptional locale!
